, #09090b 100%);color:#fafafa;padding:24px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><div style=\"max-width:860px;margin:0 auto\"><a style=\"display:inline-block;margin-bottom:24px;color:#a1a1aa;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px\" href=\"/\">← ホームに戻る</a><section style=\"border:1px solid #27272a;border-radius:20px;padding:24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(39,39,42,0.9) 0%, rgba(24,24,27,0.95) 100%);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);margin-bottom:18px\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:14px\"><div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:16px;background:#18181b;border:1px solid #27272a;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px\">☀️</div><div><p style=\"color:#71717a;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">Weather &amp; Wash Guide</p><div style=\"width:42px;height:3px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #fafafa 0%, #71717a 100%);margin-top:10px\"></div></div></div><h1 style=\"font-size:32px;margin:0 0 10px 0;line-height:1.2\">天気・洗車ガイド</h1><p style=\"color:#a1a1aa;margin:0\">現在地とお気に入り地点を切り替えて、天気と洗車おすすめ度を確認</p></section><section style=\"border:1px solid #27272a;border-radius:20px;padding:18px;background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(39,39,42,0.9) 0%, rgba(24,24,27,0.95) 100%);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);margin-bottom:16px\"><p style=\"color:#71717a;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">Location Switch</p><div style=\"width:42px;height:3px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #fafafa 0%, #71717a 100%);margin-top:10px\"></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px\"><button style=\"padding:10px 14px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #60a5fa;background:#172554;color:#eff6ff;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700;font-size:14px\">現在地</button></div><div style=\"margin-top:20px;display:grid;gap:12px\"><input placeholder=\"地点名 例: 自宅 / 洗車場 / 会社\" style=\"width:100%;padding:14px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #3f3f46;background:#09090b;color:#fafafa;outline:none;font-size:15px\" value=\"\"/><input placeholder=\"緯度 例: 38.3193\" style=\"width:100%;padding:14px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #3f3f46;background:#09090b;color:#fafafa;outline:none;font-size:15px\" value=\"\"/><input placeholder=\"経度 例: 140.8811\" style=\"width:100%;padding:14px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid #3f3f46;background:#09090b;color:#fafafa;outline:none;font-size:15px\" value=\"\"/><div style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap\"><button style=\"padding:12px 16px;border-radius:14px;border:none;background:#fafafa;color:#09090b;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px\">お気に入り地点を追加</button></div><p style=\"margin:0;color:#a1a1aa;font-size:13px\">例: 仙台市泉区付近なら 緯度 38.3193 / 経度 140.8811 あたり</p></div></section><section style=\"border:1px solid #27272a;border-radius:20px;padding:18px;background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(39,39,42,0.9) 0%, rgba(24,24,27,0.95) 100%);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);margin-bottom:16px\"><p style=\"color:#71717a;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">Target Area</p><div style=\"width:42px;height:3px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #fafafa 0%, #71717a 100%);margin-top:10px\"></div><p style=\"margin:16px 0 0 0;color:#a1a1aa\">取得地域を確認中...</p></section><section style=\"border:1px solid #27272a;border-radius:20px;padding:18px;background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(39,39,42,0.9) 0%, rgba(24,24,27,0.95) 100%);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);margin-bottom:16px\"><p style=\"color:#71717a;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0\">Today&#x27;s Wash Score</p><div style=\"width:42px;height:3px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #fafafa 0%, #71717a 100%);margin-top:10px\"></div><p style=\"margin-top:16px;color:#a1a1aa\">読み込み中...</p></secti